parsed caption:
Ohne Titel (2000); Die Skulptur aus
[Tessiner](https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kanton_Tessin "de:Kanton Tessin")
[Granit](https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Granit "de:Granit") hat keinen Titel.
Sie wurde im Jahr 2000 vom [Schweizer](https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Schweiz
"de:Schweiz") Bildhauer Beat Bösiger geschaffen und befindet sich vor dem
[Bonner](https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bonn "de:Bonn")
[Volksbank](https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volksbank_Bonn_Rhein-Sieg

file_name: File:Bert Koenders in Algeria for diplomatic relations February 2015.jpg
description: ['Algerian politician']
parsed caption:
Koenders meets Algeria's Commerce Minister Amara Benyounès

* * *

Minister Koenders bezoekt Algerije

Minister Koenders (Buitenlandse Zaken) brengt maandag 23 februari een bezoek
aan Algerije. ‘Regionale ontwikkelingen op het gebied van veiligheid en
migratie, en economische kansen zijn redenen om de relaties verder uit te
bouwen’, aldus de minister voorafgaand aan zijn vertrek.

Koenders zal ook de toenemende instabiliteit in de regio bespreken, evenals de
voortgang rond het vredesproces in Mali. ‘Algerije is een invloedrijk land in
een instabiele regio. Het is daarom goed om te zien hoe we de omliggende
landen kunnen helpen op weg naar meer stabiliteit’, zegt Koenders, die zich
grote zorgen maakt over de verslechterende situatie in Mali en Libië.

In Algiers spreekt de minister op maandag onder meer met zijn ambtgenoot
Lamamra en minister-president Sellal. Koenders: ‘Algerije is het grootste land
van Afrika en een buurland van de Europese Unie. Het is daarom goed en nuttig
om te onderzoeken op welke gebieden we elkaar kunnen helpen en hoe we van
elkaar kunnen leren.’ Een van de onderwerpen om kennis over uit te wisselen
met Algerije is de zorg over geradicaliseerde jongeren die op jihad gaan naar
Syrië en Irak. In de gesprekken zal onder meer worden besproken hoe voorkomen
kan worden dat jongeren radicaliseren en hoe bilateraal en internationaal
samengewerkt wordt om radicalisering tegen te gaan.

Minister Koenders zal tijdens zijn bezoek ook spreken met maatschappelijke
organisaties die zich inzetten voor het verbeteren van de
mensenrechtensituatie. ‘Een goede bilaterale relatie biedt niet alleen de
ruimte om op gedeelde belangen nauwere samenwerking aan te gaan, het biedt ook
de mogelijkheid om zaken te bespreken waarover de meningen uiteen lopen.’

Onlangs bracht minister Ploumen (Buitenlandse Handel en
Ontwikkelingssamenwerking) met een groep bedrijven een bezoek aan Algerije.

The fastest I've ever seen a 73 move giving the passengers waiting on Shortlands station platform a bit of a shock as it raced through with squeaky horn going.

73964 GBBR

GB Railfreight's re-engineered class 73 number 73964 (previously E6031, 73124 and <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/99279135@N05/12665910213">73205</a>) named "Jeanette" travels light engine from Loughborough Brush Works to Tonbridge West Yard on 1 April 2015. E6031 (works number E3593/E363) was built at the English Electric Vulcan Foundry in 1966. description: ['American  journalist']
parsed caption:
A journalist trained as a lawyer, [Sarah
Jeong](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sarah_Jeong "w:Sarah Jeong") writes about
technology, policy, and law as contributing editor at Motherboard. Last year,
she published The Internet Is Garbage, a deep dive into online harassment, the
failed attempts to remove it from online platforms, and the balance between
free speech and thoughtful community management.

Recorded in September 2016 at XOXO, an experimental festival celebrating
independently produced art and technology in Portland, Oregon. For more, visit
<http://xoxofest.com>.

(Description above transcribed faithfully from source YouTube description,
found [here](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bltoTMJZetc). Screenshot taken at
16:39.)

description: ['stadium in the Saxon city of Dresden']
parsed caption:
Umbau zum Multifunktionsarena mit dem Schwerpunkt Leichtathletik bis zu 15.000
Zuschauern Platz bieten. Innerhalb des Gebäudes der Haupttribüne sind außerdem
der Bau einer Fechterhalle, multifunktionale Sporträume, Fitness- und
Tagungsräume, Platz für Sportmedizin, Büros der Vereine sowie Gastronomie
vorgesehen. Eine Plaza als zentraler Eingangsbereich zum gesamten Sportpark
Ostra ergänzt die Neubau-Umsetzung. Der bestehende Finanzierungsrahmen beläuft
sich auf 37,3 Millionen Euro, wovon die Stadt Dresden 33,3 Millionen Euro
trägt.

file_name: File:The South Birmingham Community Health National Health Service Trust (Establishment) Order 1993 (UKSI 1993-2543).pdf
depicts: ['The South Birmingham Community Health National Health Service Trust (Establishment) Order 1993']
description: ['UK Statutory Instrument 1993\xa0No. 2543']
parsed caption:
This Order establishes the South Birmingham Community Health National Health
Service Trust, an NHS trust provided for in section 5 of the National Health
Service and Community Care Act 1990. It also provides for the functions of the
trust both before (article 6) and after (article 3) its operational date (the
date on which it assumes all its functions). It specifies the operational date
and the accounting date of the trust (article 5) and makes provision for
assistance to the trust by health authorities before its operational date
(article 7). It specifies the value of assets in excess of which the Secretary
of State is to consider the disposal of the asset (article 8).

description: ['star at the centre of the Solar System']
parsed caption:
AIA 0211 channel (as well as AIA 335) highlights the active region of the
outer atmosphere of the Sun - the corona. Active regions, solar flares, and
coronal mass ejections will appear bright here. The dark areas - called
coronal holes - are places where very little radiation is emitted, yet are the
main source of solar wind particles.

**Where:** Active regions of the corona

**Wavelength:** 211 angstroms (0.0000000211 m) = Extreme Ultraviolet

**Primary ions seen:** 13 times ionized iron (Fe XIV)

**Characteristic temperature:** 2 million K (3.6 million F)

file_name: File:1920 Barney Oldfield Marvin D Boland Collection G521079.jpg
description: ['American racing driver (1878-1946)']
parsed caption:
Veteran early race car driver and "Grand Old Man" of racing, Barney Oldfield
was in Tacoma in July of 1920 to serve as pacesetter for the Tacoma Classic on
the 5th. He was photographed with his signature cigar behind the wheel of an
automobile. During his career as a driver, Oldfield broke speed records, won
match races and put on exhibitions. A consummate showman, he helped develop
the image of auto racing as dangerous and exotic and its drivers as outlaws,
and made a fortune doing it. His name became synonymous with the sport. He
retired in 1918 from racing, but continued public appearances. He died in
1946. (TDL 7/4/1920, pg. 1C) Speedway 082

description: ['star at the centre of the Solar System']
parsed caption:
AIA 0211 channel (as well as AIA 335) highlights the active region of the
outer atmosphere of the Sun - the corona. Active regions, solar flares, and
coronal mass ejections will appear bright here. The dark areas - called
coronal holes - are places where very little radiation is emitted, yet are the
main source of solar wind particles.

**Where:** Active regions of the corona

**Wavelength:** 211 angstroms (0.0000000211 m) = Extreme Ultraviolet

**Primary ions seen:** 13 times ionized iron (Fe XIV)

**Characteristic temperature:** 2 million K (3.6 million F)

file_name: File:Halvor Myrvoll som soldat i den norske hæren, 1920.jpg
description: ['Norwegian skier']
parsed caption:
Halvor Orebakken (later Myrvoll) as a soldier in the Norwegian Army, 1920. He
was nationally known as a skier in the 1920s and took part in several national
competitions. He was also a pacifist, poet, and socialist, remembered for his
anti-war poems "I kongens klær" ("In the king's clothes" and "Ein ungdom spør"
("A youth asks").

description: ['a tour of any type of destination led by a guide', 'municipality in Andalusia, southern Spain']
parsed caption:
Este archivo representa el logo oficial de Córdoba a Pie, una empresa
especializada en ofrecer visitas guiadas por los monumentos y lugares de
interés más emblemáticos de Córdoba, España. Fundada en 2014, Córdoba a Pie
busca enriquecer la experiencia cultural de turistas y residentes locales a
través de recorridos guiados por expertos, destacando la rica historia y
patrimonio cultural de la región. Este logo es utilizado en todas las
comunicaciones oficiales, materiales promocionales y plataformas digitales de
la empresa para identificar y representar la marca Córdoba a Pie.

description: ['star at the centre of the Solar System']
parsed caption:
AIA 0094 channel (as well as AIA 131) is designed to study solar flares. It
measures extremely hot temperatures around 6 million Kelvin (10.8 million F).
It can take images every 2 seconds (instead of 10) in a reduced field of view
in order to look at flares in more detail.

**Where:** Flaring regions of the corona

**Wavelength:** 94 angstroms (0.0000000094 m) = Extreme Ultraviolet/soft
X-rays

**Primary ions seen:** 17 times ionized iron (Fe XVIII)

**Characteristic temperature:** 6 million K (10.8 million F)

This Order revokes the Undersized Whiting Order 1992 (“the 1992 Order”),
except in so far as it forms part of the law of Scotland or has effect in
relation to Wales (article 2). The 1992 Order prescribed minimum sizes for the
landing and sale in Great Britain, and for carriage on a British fishing boat,
of whiting (Merlangius merlangus). It also made related provision for
enforcement.

description: ['star at the centre of the Solar System']
parsed caption:
AIA 1700 channel (as well as AIA 1600) often shows a web-like pattern of
bright areas that highlight places where bundles of magnetic fields lines are
concentrated. However, small areas with a lot of field lines will appear
black, usually near sunspots and active regions.

**Where:** Temperature minimum and photosphere

**Wavelength:** 1700 angstroms (0.00000017 m) = Far Ultraviolet

**Primary ions seen:** Continuum

**Characteristic temperature:** 6,000 K (11,000 F)

description: ['star at the centre of the Solar System']
parsed caption:
HMI measures the Sun's magnetic field over the entire visible disk with 1 arc
second resolution. The line of sight magnetic field color table is designed to
visually show structure at both high and low field values.

Field strengths <24 G are shades of gray. Positive Field Values are green and
blue. Negative field values are yellow and red.

Weak field regions appear mostly yellow or green. Increasingly positive values
range from dark green to bright green at 236G. Negative values move from
bright yellow to orange at -236G.

There is a sharp discontinuity in color at 236G.

Positive or negative polarity sunspots and other strong field regions will
appear blue or red with dark umbrae.

There are 254 defined colors symmetrically arranged around the zero point.

The 127 positive include 2 darkening gray, 18 brightening green, and 110
darkening blue.

The 127 negative include 2 brightening gray, 18 darkening yellow, and 107
darkening red.

Nominally, each color spans a range of ~11.81 G and the color table extends
from -1500 to 1500 G.

West Coast.

description: ['Italian comune']
parsed caption:
Il monumento rappresentato è Piazza Unità d'Italia, Novellara in provincia di
Reggio Emilia (Italia). Ci tengo a dedicare questa foto a Daniela e Luisa, che
sono state le mie insegnanti di italiano e storia alle scuole elementari;
entrambe hanno contribuito alla mia crescita personale nel periodi in cui i
bambini assorbono più nozioni. Ho scelto di mettere in primo piano un libro,
che mi ricorda molto Daniela, la quale mi ha insegnato ad amare la lettura e
la scrittura; in secondo piano, ma non per importanza, i monumenti tipici di
Novellara, i quali mi hanno fatto pensare a Luisa, senza la quale ad oggi non
saprei molto sulla storia dei Gonzaga.

description: ['Japanese politician']
parsed caption:
平成２２年６月８日、菅内閣が発足しました。

新内閣が組閣され、総理大臣官邸にて、仙谷由人新内閣官房長官から閣僚名簿が発表されました。

その後、菅直人新内閣総理大臣が記者会見を行い、夜には、宮中において内閣総理大臣の親任式及び国務大臣の認証式が行われ、正式に菅内閣が発足しました。

続いて、総理大臣官邸において初閣議を開催、引き続き記念撮影を行いました。

description: ['star at the centre of the Solar System']
parsed caption:
AIA 0193 channel highlights the outer atmosphere of the Sun - called the
corona - as well as hot flare plasma. Hot active regions, solar flares, and
coronal mass ejections will appear bright here. The dark areas - called
coronal holes - are places where very little radiation is emitted, yet are the
main source of solar wind particles.

**Where:** Corona and hot flare plasma

**Wavelength:** 193 angstroms (0.0000000193 m) = Extreme Ultraviolet

**Primary ions seen:** 11 times ionized iron (Fe XII)

**Characteristic temperature:** 1.25 million K (2.25 million F)

file_name: File:Indonesia's Minister of Health Dr. Nafsiah Mboi.jpg
description: ['17th Health Minister of Indonesia, Indonesian politician and physician']
parsed caption:
At the opening reception of the GHSA meeting in Jakarta August 19, Indonesia's
Minister of Health Dr. Nafsiah Mboi highlighted the importance of partnerships
as the basis on which global health security can be accelerated through the
GHSA. The meeting includes presentations and work group meetings in which 30+
countries and 6 international organizations will participate including WHO,
FAO, and OIE. The meeting is focused on One Health, the intersection of human
and animal health and required multi-sector coordination needed to effectively
prevent, rapidly detect, and effectively respond to infectious disease
outbreaks.

description: ['Brazilian journalist']
parsed caption:
Comissão de Ciência, Tecnologia, Inovação, Comunicação e Informática (CCT)
realiza audiência pública interativa para tratar sobre projetos de cooperação
científica e tecnológica entre Brasil e Israel na área de tecnologia da água e
demais assuntos constantes de carta anexa ao RCT 1/2018, encaminhada pela
Embaixada de Israel.

Presidente da CCT, senador Otto Alencar (PSD-BA) recebe homenagem da Embaixada
de Israel.

Participam: embaixador de Israel no Brasil, Yossi Shelley; ministro da Ciência
e Tecnologia do Estado de Israel, Ofir Akunis; senador Lasier Martins (PSD-
RS).

Foto: Roque de Sá/Agência Senado

description: ['dictator of Germany from 1933 to 1945']
parsed caption:
Cet arbre généalogique simplifié mentionne uniquement les personnes
principales de la généalogie d’Hitler et de ses proches parents, à
l’exclusion.

  * des enfants morts en bas âge (avant la puberté)
  * des ascendants lointains
  * des descendants de collatéraux ayant vécus ou vivants après 1950.

Pour plus de détails ou précisions se reporter à la page de Wikipedia en
allemand: [Hitler
(Familie)](//commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?title=Hitler_\(Familie\)&action=edit&redlink=1
"Hitler \(Familie\) \(page does not exist\)")

Le père d’ Alois Schicklgruber né de Maria Schicklgruber en 1837, n’est pas
identifié de façon certaine. Ce peut être:

  * Johann Georg Hiedler marié à Maria Schiclkgruber en 1842, qui n'a pas formellement reconnu l'enfant de son vivant.
  * Johann Nepomuk Hiedler son plus jeune frère suivant certains historiens
  * Une autre personne objet de diverses spéculations et controverses

Alois Schiclkgruber, père d' Adolf Hitler change de nom pour celui de Hitler
en 1877 à 40 ans soit :

  * 30 ans après le décès de sa mère
  * 20 ans après le décès de son père légalisé

Même en admettant des délais importants de procédures administratives à
l'époque en Autriche Impériale cela semble bizarre.

Maria Schicklgruber a toujours refusé de révéler le nom du père de son seul
fils Alois

file_name: File:New York City St. Patrick's Day Parade DVIDS261052.jpg
description: ['National Historic and New York City Landmark']
parsed caption:
The Quantico Marine Corps Band performed inside the 69th Regiment Armory, a
National Historical Landmark, and home of the New York Army National GuardÕs
1st Battalion, 69th Infantry Regiment. The band was invited inside after they
finished marching in the 249th St. Patrick's Day Parade, here, March 17. The
"Fighting 69th" has been leading the St. Patrick's Day Parade since 1851. A
contingent of more than 300 Marines, including the Quantico Marine Corps Band,
ceremonial marchers from Marine Barracks Washington, active and reserve
Marines and Marine Corps League members from the New York area, marched in
honor of Grand Marshal Raymond W. Kelly, New York City Police Commissioner and
retired Marine Corps colonel.

description: ['star at the centre of the Solar System']
parsed caption:
AIA 0304 channel is especially good at showing areas where cooler dense plumes
of plasma (filaments and prominences) are located above the visible surface of
the Sun. Many of these features either can't be seen or appear as dark lines
in the other channels. The bright areas show places where the plasma has a
high density.

**Where:** Upper chromosphere and lower transition region

**Wavelength:** 304 angstroms (0.0000000304 m) = Extreme Ultraviolet

**Primary ions seen:** singly ionized helium (He II)

**Characteristic temperature:** 50,000 K (90,000 F)

Joseph H. Brown Elementary School is an elementary school at 3600 Stanwood
Street, Philadelphia, PA 19136 in the Holmesburg neighborhood of Northeast
Philadelphia, ates, currently serving students from kindergarten to sixth
grade. The current school building was constructed in 1937, replacing an
earlier building on the same site. It was designed by Irwin T. Catharine, then
the Philadelphia School District's main architect, and is an exemplar of the
Art Deco and Moderne schools of architecture.
